happening behind the scenes

00:03:26.300 --> 00:03:27.710 align:middle line:90%
but they were covered up.

00:03:27.710 --> 00:03:31.340 align:middle line:84%
But now they're being
exposed and confronted.

00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:34.580 align:middle line:84%
