may seem daunting.

00:04:03.630 --> 00:04:06.810 align:middle line:84%
But when we take the
approach of an alchemist,

00:04:06.810 --> 00:04:11.510 align:middle line:84%
a new vision and
clarity emerges.

00:04:11.510 --> 00:04:13.610 align:middle line:84%
To illustrate this
journey, let's compare it

00:04:13.610 --> 00:04:16.490 align:middle line:84%
to the metamorphosis of
a caterpillar becoming

00:04:16.490 --> 00:04:18.560 align:middle line:90%
a butterfly.

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:20.720 align:middle line:84%
In the beginning,
the caterpillar

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:24.800 align:middle line:84%
lives most of its life
consuming and growing fat

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:29.060 align:middle line:84%
off of the land, until one day
some kind of internal clock

00:04:29.060 --> 00:04:30.430 align:middle line:90%
goes off.

00:04:30.430 --> 00:04:34.100 align:middle line:84%
And as the caterpillar reaches
a certain level of maturity,

00:04:34.100 --> 00:04:38.390 align:middle line:84%
at this point its normal
function starts slowing down

00:04:38.390 --> 00:04:42.440 align:middle line:84%
and it becomes a struggle
to carry on as usual.

00:04:42.440 --> 00:04:46.040 align:middle line:84%
So the caterpillar finds
a nice little spot to rest

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:49.320 align:middle line:84%
and spins itself a
comfy little cocoon.

00:04:49.320 --> 00:04:51.320 align:middle line:84%
And within this
cocoon, or chrysalis,

00:04:51.320 --> 00:04:54.860 align:middle line:84%
an alchemical process
starts to take place.

00:04:54.860 --> 00:04:58.220 align:middle line:84%
It begins with the old
structure of the caterpillar

00:04:58.220 --> 00:05:02.480 align:middle line:84%
breaking down and going
through a form of death.

00:05:02.480 --> 00:05:05.780 align:middle line:84%
This initial breakdown relates
to the calcination stage

00:05:05.780 --> 00:05:06.950 align:middle line:90%
of alchemy.

00:05:06.950 --> 00:05:10.390 align:middle line:90%
It's literally digesting itself.

00:05:10.390 --> 00:05:14.300 align:middle line:84%
As the caterpillar's cells
dissolve into a soupy mess,

00:05:14.300 --> 00:05:18.350 align:middle line:84%
it enters into the second
stage of disillusion.

00:05:18.350 --> 00:05:21.830 align:middle line:84%
Within our society, we
might compare the old form

00:05:21.830 --> 00:05:25.130 align:middle line:84%
of the caterpillar to the
structures and institutions

00:05:25.130 --> 00:05:28.460 align:middle line:84%
born out of the
Industrial Revolution.

00:05:28.460 --> 00:05:31.790 align:middle line:84%
These systems dominated our
way of perceiving and operating

00:05:31.790 --> 00:05:34.110 align:middle line:90%
for a long time.

00:05:34.110 --> 00:05:36.710 align:middle line:84%
But since the new
Millennium, these structures

00:05:36.710 --> 00:05:39.290 align:middle line:84%
are starting to
crumble, and we've

00:05:39.290 --> 00:05:43.130 align:middle line:84%
been shifting into
a new paradigm way.

00:05:43.130 --> 00:05:46.400 align:middle line:84%
We see this breakdown happening
within the worlds of finance,

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:48.950 align:middle line:84%
government, business,
education, and

00:05:48.950 --> 00:05:52.010 align:middle line:90%
many other societal systems.

00:05:52.010 --> 00:05:55.010 align:middle line:84%
Things are really
in flux right now,

00:05:55.010 --> 00:05:58.160 align:middle line:84%
and visionaries of all
fields are literally

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:01.670 align:middle line:84%
looking for the next
big, disruptive idea.

00:06:01.670 --> 00:06:04.040 align:middle line:84%
We want change to
happen, and there's

00:06:04.040 --> 00:06:08.130 align:middle line:84%
a lot of progress being
made behind the scenes.

00:06:08.130 --> 00:06:12.250 align:middle line:84%
But there's also those
who don't want change.

00:06:12.250 --> 00:06:14.250 align:middle line:84%
They want things
to stay the same

00:06:14.250 --> 00:06:17.280 align:middle line:90%
according to the old paradigm.

00:06:17.280 --> 00:06:19.620 align:middle line:84%
We can compare
people within society

00:06:19.620 --> 00:06:22.080 align:middle line:90%
to the cells of the caterpillar.

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:25.680 align:middle line:84%
Some people think the old
structure worked just fine

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:29.520 align:middle line:84%
and that it provided safety,
security, and control.

00:06:29.520 --> 00:06:32.460 align:middle line:84%
Everyone knew their
place and their duty.

00:06:32.460 --> 00:06:35.760 align:middle line:84%
These people tend to cling
to that old structure

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:38.820 align:middle line:90%
and fight for its survival.

00:06:38.820 --> 00:06:41.790 align:middle line:84%
Other people feel
the system is flawed

00:06:41.790 --> 00:06:45.150 align:middle line:84%
and are ready to find a
better way of operating.

00:06:45.150 --> 00:06:47.550 align:middle line:10%
These are the innovators,
the visionaries,

00:06:47.550 --> 00:06:52.020 align:middle line:10%
and the change agents who
actively work for progress.

00:06:52.020 --> 00:06:55.020 align:middle line:84%
Then we have the people who fall
somewhere in the middle, who

00:06:55.020 --> 00:06:58.090 align:middle line:90%
tend to go with the status quo.

00:06:58.090 --> 00:07:00.150 align:middle line:84%
Most of the time,
the comfort zone

00:07:00.150 --> 00:07:05.220 align:middle line:84%
wins out because change requires
a lot of energy and discipline.

00:07:05.220 --> 00:07:08.580 align:middle line:84%
But when the comfort zone
gets ripped away from us,

00:07:08.580 --> 00:07:12.420 align:middle line:84%
like what happens in the
calcination stage of alchemy,

00:07:12.420 --> 00:07:17.520 align:middle line:84%
things stop feeling so safe and
the system becomes agitated.

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:20.640 align:middle line:84%
As this breakdown happens
within the caterpillar,

00:07:20.640 --> 00:07:23.190 align:middle line:84%
the old cells act
like they're dying

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:26.640 align:middle line:90%
and they go into survival mode.

00:07:26.640 --> 00:07:30.510 align:middle line:84%
At the same time that the old
structure starts breaking down,

00:07:30.510 --> 00:07:34.410 align:middle line:84%
a new type of cell
appears on the scene.

00:07:34.410 --> 00:07:37.460 align:middle line:84%
These new cells are
called imaginal cells,

00:07:37.460 --> 00:07:39.990 align:middle line:84%
and they start showing
up in greater numbers.

00:07:39.990 --> 00:07:43.470 align:middle line:84%
And since they're different
from the old cells,

00:07:43.470 --> 00:07:47.490 align:middle line:84%
they're perceived as a
threat to the system.

00:07:47.490 --> 00:07:50.550 align:middle line:84%
It's as if the old cells think
that the imaginal cells are

00:07:50.550 --> 00:07:55.090 align:middle line:84%
like a virus, and so they
attack and try to kill them off.

00:07:55.090 --> 00:07:57.090 align:middle line:84%
This is where the
cells enter into what

00:07:57.090 --> 00:08:01.060 align:middle line:84%
we call the separation stage
of the alchemical process.

00:08:01.060 --> 00:08:04.410 align:middle line:84%
The imaginal cells need to
separate out from the old cells

00:08:04.410 --> 00:08:07.040 align:middle line:90%
in order to survive.

00:08:07.040 --> 00:08:11.450 align:middle line:84%
Fortunately, the caterpillar's
DNA has shifted its expression,

00:08:11.450 --> 00:08:13.220 align:middle line:84%
and it's putting
out the instructions

00:08:13.220 --> 00:08:15.870 align:middle line:90%
to create more imaginal cells.

00:08:15.870 --> 00:08:17.930 align:middle line:84%
They're part of the
blueprint, as they

00:08:17.930 --> 00:08:19.990 align:middle line:90%
were from the beginning.

00:08:19.990 --> 00:08:22.130 align:middle line:84%
And as more and more
come onto the scene,

00:08:22.130 --> 00:08:27.270 align:middle line:84%
they start grouping together
and gain strength in numbers.

00:08:27.270 --> 00:08:31.570 align:middle line:84%
Now, at some point the imaginal
cells reach a critical mass.

00:08:31.570 --> 00:08:33.520 align:middle line:84%
They realize they
don't have to do

00:08:33.520 --> 00:08:36.010 align:middle line:90%
and be everything on their own.

00:08:36.010 --> 00:08:38.140 align:middle line:84%
They can start to
specialize and create

00:08:38.140 --> 00:08:40.570 align:middle line:90%
new forms and structures.

00:08:40.570 --> 00:08:44.020 align:middle line:84%
This structure is guided by
a clear vision within the DNA

00:08:44.020 --> 00:08:47.260 align:middle line:84%
blueprint, and soon the
form of the butterfly

00:08:47.260 --> 00:08:49.900 align:middle line:90%
starts taking shape.

00:08:49.900 --> 00:08:52.360 align:middle line:84%
This brings us to
the conjunction stage

00:08:52.360 --> 00:08:54.470 align:middle line:90%
of the alchemical process.

00:08:54.470 --> 00:08:58.780 align:middle line:84%
The imaginal cells unite
around this new common vision,

00:08:58.780 --> 00:09:01.780 align:middle line:84%
and the old caterpillar
cells, still clinging

00:09:01.780 --> 00:09:04.540 align:middle line:84%
to the old crumbling
system, start noticing

00:09:04.540 --> 00:09:06.970 align:middle line:90%
something new is happening.

00:09:06.970 --> 00:09:09.010 align:middle line:84%
They see that
whatever's going on

00:09:09.010 --> 00:09:12.430 align:middle line:84%
with those imaginal cells
seems to be working.

00:09:12.430 --> 00:09:14.470 align:middle line:84%
And then, some of
the caterpillar cells

00:09:14.470 --> 00:09:17.380 align:middle line:84%
start to jump ship and
join the new system

00:09:17.380 --> 00:09:20.490 align:middle line:90%
by repurposing themselves.

00:09:20.490 --> 00:09:23.360 align:middle line:84%
For example, a
digestive cell can still

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:25.610 align:middle line:90%
function as a digestive cell.

00:09:25.610 --> 00:09:29.030 align:middle line:84%
An immunity cell can still
function as an immunity cell.

00:09:29.030 --> 00:09:33.790 align:middle line:84%
They just need to reorient
into the new system.

00:09:33.790 --> 00:09:36.590 align:middle line:84%
And as the caterpillar's
cells assume the tasks

00:09:36.590 --> 00:09:40.460 align:middle line:84%
that they were designed to
do within this new structure,

00:09:40.460 --> 00:09:42.710 align:middle line:84%
this frees up the
imagine all cells

00:09:42.710 --> 00:09:45.423 align:middle line:90%
to now specialize even further.

00:09:45.423 --> 00:09:47.090 align:middle line:84%
They start to form
the new elements that

00:09:47.090 --> 00:09:49.490 align:middle line:90%
are unique to the butterfly.

00:09:49.490 --> 00:09:52.880 align:middle line:84%
Now they start to develop the
wings, the antenna, and so

00:09:52.880 --> 00:09:54.650 align:middle line:90%
forth.

00:09:54.650 --> 00:09:58.880 align:middle line:84%
This harmonizing and
cooperation of opposing elements

00:09:58.880 --> 00:10:02.630 align:middle line:84%
is what the conjunction
stage is all about.

00:10:02.630 --> 00:10:05.360 align:middle line:84%
All of the essential elements
are identified and brought

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:08.280 align:middle line:90%
together in harmony.

00:10:08.280 --> 00:10:11.060 align:middle line:90%
But we're not done yet.

00:10:11.060 --> 00:10:14.270 align:middle line:84%
If we were to stop the process
here and try to open up

00:10:14.270 --> 00:10:16.670 align:middle line:84%
the chrysalis to help
that butterfly out,

00:10:16.670 --> 00:10:19.850 align:middle line:84%
it would be too premature and
that butterfly would never

00:10:19.850 --> 00:10:23.120 align:middle line:84%
fly, let alone it
might not even survive.

00:10:23.120 --> 00:10:26.390 align:middle line:84%
So the metamorphosis must
continue until that butterfly

00:10:26.390 --> 00:10:29.600 align:middle line:90%
comes to full maturity.

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:33.260 align:middle line:84%
What happens next is that the
old caterpillar cells that

00:10:33.260 --> 00:10:36.170 align:middle line:84%
fail to align within
the new structure

00:10:36.170 --> 00:10:39.440 align:middle line:84%
start to dissolve into
the alchemical soup

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:41.630 align:middle line:90%
and eventually die off.

00:10:41.630 --> 00:10:43.370 align:middle line:84%
This alchemical
soup then becomes

00:10:43.370 --> 00:10:46.880 align:middle line:84%
what fuels the newly
emerging system until it

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:51.050 align:middle line:90%
reaches a state of maturity.

00:10:51.050 --> 00:10:55.040 align:middle line:84%
This brings us to the
fermentation stage of alchemy.

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:59.810 align:middle line:84%
It's both a maturing of the new
form and a death of the old.

00:10:59.810 --> 00:11:04.490 align:middle line:84%
To ferment something means to
allow it to mature to the point

00:11:04.490 --> 00:11:08.260 align:middle line:84%
where anything that is
corruptible rots away.

00:11:08.260 --> 00:11:11.750 align:middle line:84%
And in this stage, we're
forced to go deeper and address

00:11:11.750 --> 00:11:14.660 align:middle line:84%
some of the core structures
and impurities remaining

00:11:14.660 --> 00:11:17.020 align:middle line:90%
on more subtle levels.

00:11:17.020 --> 00:11:21.940 align:middle line:84%
Anything that's not aligned
with the purest essence must go.

00:11:21.940 --> 00:11:24.760 align:middle line:84%
This includes the remnants
of the old structure,

00:11:24.760 --> 00:11:27.595 align:middle line:84%
with its corruption
and limitations.

00:11:27.595 --> 00:11:30.760 align:middle line:84%
Now, as you can imagine,
it takes a lot more effort

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:33.340 align:middle line:84%
to root out those
subtle impurities

00:11:33.340 --> 00:11:35.650 align:middle line:90%
and corrupt elements.

00:11:35.650 --> 00:11:37.960 align:middle line:84%
The secret to
moving this process

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:42.100 align:middle line:84%
along is to introduce
a gentle heat.

00:11:42.100 --> 00:11:46.180 align:middle line:84%
For the butterfly, it's the
heat of the sun or an incubator

00:11:46.180 --> 00:11:49.000 align:middle line:90%
gently warming the chrysalis.

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:53.890 align:middle line:84%
For us, it's fueled by the fires
of devotion and higher ideal

00:11:53.890 --> 00:11:56.470 align:middle line:90%
to that greater vision.

00:11:56.470 --> 00:11:59.800 align:middle line:84%
It takes discipline,
patience, and dedication

00:11:59.800 --> 00:12:01.810 align:middle line:84%
to make it through
this stage, though.

00:12:01.810 --> 00:12:04.350 align:middle line:90%


00:12:04.350 --> 00:12:08.230 align:middle line:84%
How do we know when the
fermentation stage is done?

00:12:08.230 --> 00:12:11.200 align:middle line:84%
Well, in the metamorphosis
of the butterfly,

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:15.460 align:middle line:84%
this would be when the wing
structures in all their beauty

00:12:15.460 --> 00:12:18.940 align:middle line:84%
can be seen clearly
within the chrysalis.

00:12:18.940 --> 00:12:21.920 align:middle line:84%
The new structure is no
longer just a vision,

00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:24.580 align:middle line:84%
but now it has taken
on a physical form

00:12:24.580 --> 00:12:26.860 align:middle line:90%
within the alchemical soup.

00:12:26.860 --> 00:12:30.940 align:middle line:84%
It's the proverbial light
at the end of the tunnel.

00:12:30.940 --> 00:12:34.600 align:middle line:84%
From here on out, everything
that remains is essential

00:12:34.600 --> 00:12:39.340 align:middle line:84%
and the work moves on towards
refinement and elevation.

00:12:39.340 --> 00:12:42.250 align:middle line:84%
As everything aligns
around this new structure,

00:12:42.250 --> 00:12:45.700 align:middle line:84%
the butterfly is ready to
break out of the chrysalis.

00:12:45.700 --> 00:12:49.720 align:middle line:84%
But the process is
still not complete.

00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:54.010 align:middle line:84%
The struggle to break
free is a critical step.

00:12:54.010 --> 00:12:56.020 align:middle line:84%
Through this struggle,
the butterfly

00:12:56.020 --> 00:12:58.810 align:middle line:90%
strengthens its wings.

00:12:58.810 --> 00:13:02.110 align:middle line:84%
And again, if we were to
assist the butterfly out,

00:13:02.110 --> 00:13:05.240 align:middle line:84%
the wings wouldn't be strong
enough to take flight.

00:13:05.240 --> 00:13:10.660 align:middle line:84%
So we must allow it to struggle
and become strong on its own.

00:13:10.660 --> 00:13:13.480 align:middle line:84%
This stage of the
butterfly's metamorphosis

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:15.820 align:middle line:84%
can be compared to
the alchemical stage

00:13:15.820 --> 00:13:17.590 align:middle line:90%
of distillation.

00:13:17.590 --> 00:13:21.310 align:middle line:84%
It's a stage of
re-ordering and refinement.

00:13:21.310 --> 00:13:23.950 align:middle line:84%
But in this stage, we're
no longer treating things

00:13:23.950 --> 00:13:26.400 align:middle line:90%
at just the physical level.

00:13:26.400 --> 00:13:28.750 align:middle line:84%
And that's because
to distill something

00:13:28.750 --> 00:13:31.840 align:middle line:84%
is to take whatever
emerges from the ferment

00:13:31.840 --> 00:13:35.230 align:middle line:84%
and then dissolve it
into an aqueous solution,

00:13:35.230 --> 00:13:37.720 align:middle line:84%
and then heat it
so that it rises up

00:13:37.720 --> 00:13:40.300 align:middle line:90%
into the air as a vapor.

00:13:40.300 --> 00:13:43.870 align:middle line:84%
The evaporated essence
rises to the subtle realms,

00:13:43.870 --> 00:13:47.530 align:middle line:84%
infusing consciousness
into the materia.

00:13:47.530 --> 00:13:50.980 align:middle line:84%
And then it re-condenses to
anchor those subtle energies

00:13:50.980 --> 00:13:53.710 align:middle line:90%
back into tangible form.

00:13:53.710 --> 00:13:55.930 align:middle line:84%
Distillation requires
several cycles,

00:13:55.930 --> 00:14:00.340 align:middle line:84%
infusing more and more spirit
essence into the physical.

00:14:00.340 --> 00:14:04.090 align:middle line:84%
Finally, having emerged
victoriously from the chrysalis

00:14:04.090 --> 00:14:09.220 align:middle line:84%
and solidified its new form,
the butterfly is ready to fly.

00:14:09.220 --> 00:14:11.290 align:middle line:84%
Like the phoenix
rising from the ashes,

00:14:11.290 --> 00:14:14.650 align:middle line:84%
the butterfly emerges
from that alchemical soup.

00:14:14.650 --> 00:14:18.010 align:middle line:84%
This is the final
stage of coagulation.

00:14:18.010 --> 00:14:21.940 align:middle line:84%
The butterfly has crystallized
into its final, perfected form,

00:14:21.940 --> 00:14:24.430 align:middle line:84%
and it now graces the
world with its beauty.

