discovered that the evolutionary
and transformational process

00:14:49.720 --> 00:14:52.850 align:middle line:84%
is broken down into
these seven stages.

00:14:52.850 --> 00:14:54.970 align:middle line:84%
This is a natural
process that we all

00:14:54.970 --> 00:14:57.140 align:middle line:90%
go through, all the time.

00:14:57.140 --> 00:15:00.070 align:middle line:84%
But when left to nature
alone, it usually

00:15:00.070 --> 00:15:03.790 align:middle line:84%
takes a long time
for things to evolve.

00:15:03.790 --> 00:15:05.680 align:middle line:84%
What we learn from
the alchemists of old

00:15:05.680 --> 00:15:08.620 align:middle line:84%
is how to intentionally
work with nature

00:15:08.620 --> 00:15:11.200 align:middle line:84%
to harness consciousness
and speed up

00:15:11.200 --> 00:15:14.420 align:middle line:90%
the evolutionary process.

00:15:14.420 --> 00:15:17.240 align:middle line:84%
We've been through many
cycles throughout humanity's

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:20.720 align:middle line:84%
evolution, but today
we're in the midst

00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:23.360 align:middle line:84%
of a transformational
cycle that started

00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:26.150 align:middle line:84%
at the turn of the
new Millennium.

