And this cycle is
bringing us into position

00:15:28.610 --> 00:15:32.780 align:middle line:84%
to make a great leap
into a new paradigm.

00:15:32.780 --> 00:15:35.510 align:middle line:84%
Using these metaphors of
the butterfly and alchemy,

00:15:35.510 --> 00:15:39.800 align:middle line:84%
we can reorient ourselves with
this transformational process

00:15:39.800 --> 00:15:45.490 align:middle line:84%
and gain clarity about what's
