transformation,

00:16:01.390 --> 00:16:04.120 align:middle line:84%
rather than getting caught
up in the drama of politics

00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:06.940 align:middle line:90%
or conspiracy theories.

00:16:06.940 --> 00:16:08.920 align:middle line:84%
From the Western
world perspective,

00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:11.830 align:middle line:84%
we experienced a
couple big events

00:16:11.830 --> 00:16:15.160 align:middle line:84%
that acted as catalysts for
this calcination stage that

00:16:15.160 --> 00:16:17.440 align:middle line:90%
started our current cycle.

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:21.730 align:middle line:84%
It started with the dot
com bubble burst in 1999.

00:16:21.730 --> 00:16:24.910 align:middle line:84%
And this was soon followed by
the deregulation of the banking

00:16:24.910 --> 00:16:25.990 align:middle line:90%
industry.

00:16:25.990 --> 00:16:29.410 align:middle line:84%
And then in 2001, the
world reeled from the shock

00:16:29.410 --> 00:16:32.230 align:middle line:90%
