attack, it also

00:16:44.170 --> 00:16:48.610 align:middle line:84%
stripped American citizens
of many rights and privacy.

00:16:48.610 --> 00:16:51.640 align:middle line:84%
Wars in the Middle East
led to then more deaths

00:16:51.640 --> 00:16:55.960 align:middle line:90%
and skyrocketing national debts.

00:16:55.960 --> 00:16:59.770 align:middle line:84%
Then, intense emotions were
stirred from the breakdown,

00:16:59.770 --> 00:17:03.190 align:middle line:84%
