to self-organize and express

00:18:14.070 --> 00:18:15.405 align:middle line:90%
their voice.

00:18:15.405 --> 00:18:18.990 align:middle line:84%
Now, as the social media
revolution gained momentum,

00:18:18.990 --> 00:18:23.520 align:middle line:84%
