self-organizing increased

00:18:23.520 --> 00:18:28.020 align:middle line:84%
and we transitioned into
the separation stage.

00:18:28.020 --> 00:18:31.440 align:middle line:84%
Soon, various groups
of similar agendas

00:18:31.440 --> 00:18:35.460 align:middle line:84%
