Street to the Tea Party

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:41.400 align:middle line:90%
and libertarian efforts.

00:18:41.400 --> 00:18:44.430 align:middle line:84%
And then later came the
alternative energy initiatives,

00:18:44.430 --> 00:18:46.500 align:middle line:84%
Black Lives Matter,
the Time's Up movement,

00:18:46.500 --> 00:18:49.170 align:middle line:90%
