It's time for a deep
dive into our inner self

00:23:12.630 --> 00:23:16.040 align:middle line:84%
and to seek out that
spiritual awakening.

00:23:16.040 --> 00:23:19.100 align:middle line:84%
Only when enough of us
do this individually can

00:23:19.100 --> 00:23:23.090 align:middle line:84%
we then start to
do it collectively.

00:23:23.090 --> 00:23:27.470 align:middle line:84%
If it's up to us as
individuals, where do we start?

00:23:27.470 --> 00:23:29.480 align:middle line:84%
First off, we have to
recognize where we're

00:23:29.480 --> 00:23:31.780 align:middle line:90%
at in our personal journey.

00:23:31.780 --> 00:23:33.740 align:middle line:84%
The alchemical
process gives us a map

00:23:33.740 --> 00:23:38.820 align:middle line:84%
to see where we are and shows us
what it takes to move forward.

00:23:38.820 --> 00:23:42.060 align:middle line:84%
It's very easy to get caught up
in media, and politics, and all

00:23:42.060 --> 00:23:45.060 align:middle line:84%
the fear and judgment that goes
back and forth in our world

00:23:45.060 --> 00:23:46.110 align:middle line:90%
today.

00:23:46.110 --> 00:23:49.440 align:middle line:84%
We're living in what feels like
one of the most highly charged

00:23:49.440 --> 00:23:51.810 align:middle line:90%
and polarized times.

00:23:51.810 --> 00:23:55.350 align:middle line:84%
But alchemy works through
the tension of differences,

00:23:55.350 --> 00:23:58.690 align:middle line:84%
so there's a huge
opportunity here as well.

00:23:58.690 --> 00:24:00.420 align:middle line:84%
We have the
possibility to harness

00:24:00.420 --> 00:24:05.230 align:middle line:84%
this time of high energy
and direct it in a good way.

00:24:05.230 --> 00:24:06.770 align:middle line:90%
So how do we do that?

00:24:06.770 --> 00:24:09.830 align:middle line:84%
Well, if we return to that
metaphor of the butterfly,

00:24:09.830 --> 00:24:12.900 align:middle line:84%
the imaginal cells
are the driving force

00:24:12.900 --> 00:24:15.180 align:middle line:90%
behind this transformation.

00:24:15.180 --> 00:24:19.710 align:middle line:84%
They hold a clear vision to
guide the collective shift.

00:24:19.710 --> 00:24:23.760 align:middle line:84%
So who are the imaginal
cells of today?

00:24:23.760 --> 00:24:29.060 align:middle line:84%
And what new paradigm values
do they innately align with?

00:24:29.060 --> 00:24:32.180 align:middle line:84%
There are two primary
groups driving this shift

00:24:32.180 --> 00:24:34.130 align:middle line:90%
into the new paradigm.

00:24:34.130 --> 00:24:37.550 align:middle line:84%
The first are the millennials,
or the net generation,

00:24:37.550 --> 00:24:39.830 align:middle line:84%
those who grew up
in the digital age

00:24:39.830 --> 00:24:42.770 align:middle line:84%
and are ready for
that new paradigm.

00:24:42.770 --> 00:24:46.430 align:middle line:84%
The millennials value
creativity and innovation,

00:24:46.430 --> 00:24:48.500 align:middle line:84%
and they tend to have
a degree of skepticism

00:24:48.500 --> 00:24:51.560 align:middle line:90%
about the mainstream propaganda.

00:24:51.560 --> 00:24:53.060 align:middle line:84%
They tend to do
their own research

00:24:53.060 --> 00:24:57.200 align:middle line:84%
and decide for themselves what
they think is really happening.

00:24:57.200 --> 00:25:01.550 align:middle line:84%
Growing up digital, their
brains operate in a new way,

00:25:01.550 --> 00:25:04.730 align:middle line:84%
and they have high
expectations for a faster pace

00:25:04.730 --> 00:25:07.550 align:middle line:90%
and interconnected reality.

00:25:07.550 --> 00:25:09.950 align:middle line:84%
Millennials are breaking
out of the old structure

00:25:09.950 --> 00:25:13.730 align:middle line:84%
and pursuing technology-driven
creative solutions

00:25:13.730 --> 00:25:17.420 align:middle line:90%
to the problems of the world.

00:25:17.420 --> 00:25:19.300 align:middle line:84%
The second group
of imaginal cells

00:25:19.300 --> 00:25:22.480 align:middle line:84%
are identified as the
cultural creatives.

00:25:22.480 --> 00:25:24.160 align:middle line:84%
Cultural creatives
aren't defined

00:25:24.160 --> 00:25:27.760 align:middle line:84%
by any particular
demographic, but instead they

00:25:27.760 --> 00:25:30.820 align:middle line:90%
share a common set of values.

00:25:30.820 --> 00:25:34.180 align:middle line:84%
These values tend towards
greater sustainability,

00:25:34.180 --> 00:25:37.810 align:middle line:84%
acceptance of diversity,
and greater transparency.

00:25:37.810 --> 00:25:40.960 align:middle line:84%
They embrace ideas like
conscious consumerism, greater

00:25:40.960 --> 00:25:42.565 align:middle line:90%
cooperation, and altruism.

00:25:42.565 --> 00:25:45.180 align:middle line:90%


00:25:45.180 --> 00:25:48.630 align:middle line:84%
The old paradigm, based
on separation, fear,

00:25:48.630 --> 00:25:51.120 align:middle line:90%
and nationalism, is dying.

00:25:51.120 --> 00:25:53.070 align:middle line:84%
We see a lot of it
right now, but that's

00:25:53.070 --> 00:25:55.950 align:middle line:84%
because it's in its
final death throes.

00:25:55.950 --> 00:26:01.540 align:middle line:84%
The way forward is toward
unity, not more separation.

00:26:01.540 --> 00:26:05.560 align:middle line:84%
We are a collective,
meaning we are all one.

00:26:05.560 --> 00:26:08.700 align:middle line:84%
It's time for us to
remember and embrace that.

00:26:08.700 --> 00:26:11.530 align:middle line:84%
The cultural creatives
carry these values,

00:26:11.530 --> 00:26:14.020 align:middle line:84%
and just like the imaginal
cells of the butterfly

00:26:14.020 --> 00:26:17.290 align:middle line:84%
win out in the end, so
too will these values

00:26:17.290 --> 00:26:18.145 align:middle line:90%
of the new paradigm.

00:26:18.145 --> 00:26:20.950 align:middle line:90%


00:26:20.950 --> 00:26:23.080 align:middle line:84%
The good news is
that we have a role

00:26:23.080 --> 00:26:25.263 align:middle line:90%
to play in this metamorphosis.

00:26:25.263 --> 00:26:26.680 align:middle line:84%
And through our
collective effort,

00:26:26.680 --> 00:26:29.260 align:middle line:90%
we can accelerate the shift.

00:26:29.260 --> 00:26:31.600 align:middle line:84%
The famous principle of
correspondence that states,

00:26:31.600 --> 00:26:34.930 align:middle line:84%
"as above, so below,
as below, so above".

00:26:34.930 --> 00:26:39.890 align:middle line:84%
This can also be taken to
mean, as within, so without.

00:26:39.890 --> 00:26:43.370 align:middle line:84%
What this is saying is that
the world reflects our thought

00:26:43.370 --> 00:26:44.600 align:middle line:90%
forms.

00:26:44.600 --> 00:26:46.740 align:middle line:84%
And if we wish to
change the world,

00:26:46.740 --> 00:26:49.250 align:middle line:84%
we must first change
our inner landscape

00:26:49.250 --> 00:26:51.260 align:middle line:90%
of emotions and thoughts.

00:26:51.260 --> 00:26:53.360 align:middle line:84%
We must slay our
own inner demons

00:26:53.360 --> 00:26:55.760 align:middle line:84%
and not allow ourselves
to be distracted

00:26:55.760 --> 00:26:58.220 align:middle line:90%
by outer circumstances.

00:26:58.220 --> 00:27:01.240 align:middle line:84%
The battle can only
be won on the inside.

00:27:01.240 --> 00:27:05.150 align:middle line:84%
And from there, we can
reflect to the outer.

00:27:05.150 --> 00:27:08.390 align:middle line:84%
So how do we come through
this victoriously?

00:27:08.390 --> 00:27:10.130 align:middle line:84%
Well, in the
alchemical process we

00:27:10.130 --> 00:27:13.040 align:middle line:84%
have four keys that
can help us to move

00:27:13.040 --> 00:27:15.890 align:middle line:84%
through the fermentation
stage and to rise

00:27:15.890 --> 00:27:18.530 align:middle line:90%
from the ashes like the phoenix.

00:27:18.530 --> 00:27:22.640 align:middle line:84%
Number one is to move beyond
the emotional attachments,

00:27:22.640 --> 00:27:25.960 align:middle line:90%
opinions, and negative emotions.

00:27:25.960 --> 00:27:30.930 align:middle line:84%
Number two, be honest with
ourselves and each other.

00:27:30.930 --> 00:27:34.340 align:middle line:84%
Number three, be willing to
sacrifice the ego in order

00:27:34.340 --> 00:27:37.970 align:middle line:84%
to attain a higher
purpose and glory.

00:27:37.970 --> 00:27:42.800 align:middle line:84%
And number four, connect to
the universal spiritual source

00:27:42.800 --> 00:27:48.220 align:middle line:84%
to guide, fuel, and refine
our ongoing transformation.

00:27:48.220 --> 00:27:50.590 align:middle line:84%
Accomplishing these
four steps requires

00:27:50.590 --> 00:27:54.070 align:middle line:84%
us to face our own darkness and
do some soul searching to get

00:27:54.070 --> 00:27:57.130 align:middle line:90%
clear about our core values.

00:27:57.130 --> 00:28:01.160 align:middle line:84%
The first step is to move
beyond the emotional energy.

00:28:01.160 --> 00:28:03.040 align:middle line:84%
This includes the
reactive emotions

00:28:03.040 --> 00:28:05.530 align:middle line:84%
that drove us to speak
out against the corruption

00:28:05.530 --> 00:28:07.060 align:middle line:90%
in the first place.

00:28:07.060 --> 00:28:10.790 align:middle line:84%
It's so important that we
let go of our anger, sadness,

00:28:10.790 --> 00:28:13.570 align:middle line:84%
and dissatisfaction
with the system.

00:28:13.570 --> 00:28:16.000 align:middle line:84%
Why is this such
a necessary step?

00:28:16.000 --> 00:28:19.030 align:middle line:84%
Well, when we refuse to let go
of these emotional attachments,

00:28:19.030 --> 00:28:23.080 align:middle line:84%
we get stuck in pointing the
finger and blaming others.

00:28:23.080 --> 00:28:27.760 align:middle line:84%
And we don't take responsibility
for our own actions.

00:28:27.760 --> 00:28:30.280 align:middle line:84%
These emotions, they're
a natural response

00:28:30.280 --> 00:28:32.650 align:middle line:90%
to the calcification phase.

00:28:32.650 --> 00:28:35.290 align:middle line:84%
But if we hold on to
them, they drive us

00:28:35.290 --> 00:28:39.430 align:middle line:84%
into this emotional drama
that just keeps us stuck.

00:28:39.430 --> 00:28:44.210 align:middle line:84%
It's easy to get addicted to the
drama and stop moving forward.

00:28:44.210 --> 00:28:46.350 align:middle line:90%
So how do we let go?

00:28:46.350 --> 00:28:49.780 align:middle line:84%
The disillusion stage is meant
to give us an opportunity

00:28:49.780 --> 00:28:52.660 align:middle line:84%
to discharge this
emotional build-up,

00:28:52.660 --> 00:28:56.565 align:middle line:84%
to feel, express, and let
go of that emotional energy.

00:28:56.565 --> 00:29:01.120 align:middle line:84%
And what follows is a
greater sense of clarity.

00:29:01.120 --> 00:29:03.690 align:middle line:84%
You can think of
the "e" in emotion

00:29:03.690 --> 00:29:05.530 align:middle line:90%
as standing forward Energy.

00:29:05.530 --> 00:29:09.620 align:middle line:84%
Emotions are energy that
need to be in motion.

00:29:09.620 --> 00:29:12.910 align:middle line:84%
In other words, emotions need
to be actively moved through,

00:29:12.910 --> 00:29:18.630 align:middle line:84%
expressed, and grounded in order
to be released and dissipated.

00:29:18.630 --> 00:29:21.450 align:middle line:84%
Once we move beyond
the emotional energy,

00:29:21.450 --> 00:29:24.990 align:middle line:84%
key number to challenges
us to face the truth

00:29:24.990 --> 00:29:28.320 align:middle line:84%
and be honest with
ourselves and each other.

00:29:28.320 --> 00:29:30.550 align:middle line:84%
Usually this also
involves key number three,

00:29:30.550 --> 00:29:33.180 align:middle line:84%
which is letting go of
our pride, righteousness,

00:29:33.180 --> 00:29:35.700 align:middle line:90%
and self-centered point of view.

00:29:35.700 --> 00:29:37.590 align:middle line:84%
Only then will we be
able to acknowledge

00:29:37.590 --> 00:29:40.380 align:middle line:84%
our own shortcomings
and accept and open up

00:29:40.380 --> 00:29:44.030 align:middle line:84%
to the possibility of
other perspectives.

00:29:44.030 --> 00:29:47.600 align:middle line:84%
This is how we start to realize
creative solutions that get us

00:29:47.600 --> 00:29:49.880 align:middle line:90%
out of the mess we've created.

00:29:49.880 --> 00:29:51.410 align:middle line:84%
Telling ourselves
the truth means

00:29:51.410 --> 00:29:55.940 align:middle line:84%
recognizing the places where
we've been part of the problem.

00:29:55.940 --> 00:29:58.760 align:middle line:84%
Since ancient times,
philosophers and sages

00:29:58.760 --> 00:30:00.800 align:middle line:84%
have taught that
the world outside

00:30:00.800 --> 00:30:05.250 align:middle line:84%
is simply a reflection of what's
happening within each of us.

00:30:05.250 --> 00:30:08.810 align:middle line:84%
It's up to us to do the
work to purify ourselves

00:30:08.810 --> 00:30:12.410 align:middle line:84%
so that we can then make
the change on the outside.

00:30:12.410 --> 00:30:14.540 align:middle line:84%
It's not just about
what's happening out there

00:30:14.540 --> 00:30:17.270 align:middle line:84%
and what those people
are doing wrong.

00:30:17.270 --> 00:30:20.530 align:middle line:84%
It's about what's
happening in us.

00:30:20.530 --> 00:30:22.660 align:middle line:84%
The alchemist and
their experiments

00:30:22.660 --> 00:30:24.490 align:middle line:84%
are not viewed as
separate, but are

00:30:24.490 --> 00:30:28.270 align:middle line:84%
seen as intimately
connected or entangled.

00:30:28.270 --> 00:30:31.570 align:middle line:84%
Any change that the alchemist
wants to see in their subject,

00:30:31.570 --> 00:30:35.110 align:middle line:84%
such as the world outside, they
must first realize that change

00:30:35.110 --> 00:30:37.220 align:middle line:90%
within themselves.

00:30:37.220 --> 00:30:41.560 align:middle line:84%
Only then can they create
that change in the world.

00:30:41.560 --> 00:30:44.350 align:middle line:84%
If we want to create
a golden society,

00:30:44.350 --> 00:30:47.760 align:middle line:84%
we must first attain the gold
within our own hearts, minds,

00:30:47.760 --> 00:30:49.230 align:middle line:90%
and souls.

00:30:49.230 --> 00:30:52.680 align:middle line:84%
The inner gold is the
attainment of wisdom

00:30:52.680 --> 00:30:56.740 align:middle line:84%
and the awakening of
our full potential.

00:30:56.740 --> 00:30:59.100 align:middle line:84%
This brings us to
the fourth key,

00:30:59.100 --> 00:31:02.640 align:middle line:84%
connecting to the
universal spiritual source

00:31:02.640 --> 00:31:08.300 align:middle line:84%
to guide, fuel, and refine
our ongoing transformation.

00:31:08.300 --> 00:31:12.500 align:middle line:84%
This divine source is the
secret fire of alchemists,

00:31:12.500 --> 00:31:15.290 align:middle line:84%
and it can only be
cultivated within oneself

00:31:15.290 --> 00:31:17.390 align:middle line:90%
through spiritual devotion.

00:31:17.390 --> 00:31:20.140 align:middle line:84%
True alchemical
work starts within,

00:31:20.140 --> 00:31:24.660 align:middle line:84%
and from there it moves
out into the world.

00:31:24.660 --> 00:31:28.550 align:middle line:84%
The bottom line is that we need
more people doing the work,

00:31:28.550 --> 00:31:31.670 align:middle line:84%
getting initiated, and
committing to their journey.

00:31:31.670 --> 00:31:34.640 align:middle line:84%
If we're going to make this
shift on a larger scale,

00:31:34.640 --> 00:31:37.250 align:middle line:84%
about 3% of the
population is needed

00:31:37.250 --> 00:31:40.220 align:middle line:84%
to create that
major tipping point.

00:31:40.220 --> 00:31:42.050 align:middle line:84%
This is our critical
mass level needed

00:31:42.050 --> 00:31:44.960 align:middle line:84%
for a spontaneous evolution
and the up-leveling

00:31:44.960 --> 00:31:48.090 align:middle line:90%
of human consciousness.

00:31:48.090 --> 00:31:51.750 align:middle line:84%
3% of the population
may seem daunting.

00:31:51.750 --> 00:31:54.570 align:middle line:84%
The good news is that
we don't need to reach

00:31:54.570 --> 00:31:56.940 align:middle line:90%
that many people to begin with.

00:31:56.940 --> 00:31:59.010 align:middle line:84%
We just need to reach
the right people who

00:31:59.010 --> 00:32:01.260 align:middle line:84%
can be the ones
to tip the scales

00:32:01.260 --> 00:32:04.350 align:middle line:84%
that lead towards the
snowballing effect to take us

00:32:04.350 --> 00:32:06.490 align:middle line:90%
to the tipping point.

00:32:06.490 --> 00:32:08.680 align:middle line:84%
In Malcolm Gladwell's
book, "The Tipping Point",

00:32:08.680 --> 00:32:10.390 align:middle line:84%
he talks about three
types of people

00:32:10.390 --> 00:32:13.720 align:middle line:84%
that are at the core
of any social movement.

00:32:13.720 --> 00:32:16.720 align:middle line:84%
These are the types of people
that we need to find and bring

00:32:16.720 --> 00:32:19.380 align:middle line:90%
toward this level of awareness.

00:32:19.380 --> 00:32:21.130 align:middle line:84%
So if you might be one
of those, or if you

00:32:21.130 --> 00:32:23.890 align:middle line:84%
know of anyone who fits
these characteristics,

00:32:23.890 --> 00:32:28.590 align:middle line:84%
then introduce them to these
teachings and concepts.

00:32:28.590 --> 00:32:31.380 align:middle line:84%
These people are different
types of influencers

00:32:31.380 --> 00:32:35.070 align:middle line:84%
who can help us reach
the tipping point faster.

00:32:35.070 --> 00:32:38.070 align:middle line:84%
Maybe some of you watching
it fit these categories

00:32:38.070 --> 00:32:40.240 align:middle line:90%
or you know who do.

00:32:40.240 --> 00:32:41.730 align:middle line:90%
Who are they?

00:32:41.730 --> 00:32:45.390 align:middle line:84%
Well, the first group
he calls the connectors.

00:32:45.390 --> 00:32:49.470 align:middle line:84%
Connectors are naturally social
and they love to meet people.

00:32:49.470 --> 00:32:52.710 align:middle line:84%
They're incredibly
charismatic, and good all kinds

00:32:52.710 --> 00:32:54.960 align:middle line:84%
of social interactions,
and they enjoy

00:32:54.960 --> 00:32:57.850 align:middle line:84%
the process of randomly
getting to know people

00:32:57.850 --> 00:33:00.540 align:middle line:84%
and then will maintain
those connections.

00:33:00.540 --> 00:33:03.690 align:middle line:84%
Connectors also love helping
you connect to the right people

00:33:03.690 --> 00:33:05.860 align:middle line:90%
in their inner circle.

00:33:05.860 --> 00:33:09.660 align:middle line:84%
Now the second group
he terms as the mavens.

00:33:09.660 --> 00:33:13.680 align:middle line:84%
Mavens are social, but they're
more information oriented.

00:33:13.680 --> 00:33:17.040 align:middle line:84%
They seek out knowledge
in a variety of topics

00:33:17.040 --> 00:33:20.820 align:middle line:84%
and will learn the ins, and
outs, and all the details.

00:33:20.820 --> 00:33:23.430 align:middle line:84%
They're the ones who dive
in to do the research

00:33:23.430 --> 00:33:26.400 align:middle line:84%
and find out where
to go, what to buy,

00:33:26.400 --> 00:33:30.030 align:middle line:84%
and where you're really
going to get your best value.

00:33:30.030 --> 00:33:32.970 align:middle line:84%
They love to do this research
and then make recommendations

00:33:32.970 --> 00:33:34.470 align:middle line:90%
for other people.

00:33:34.470 --> 00:33:36.990 align:middle line:84%
And you can trust them because
you know that they've really

00:33:36.990 --> 00:33:38.610 align:middle line:90%
done their homework.

00:33:38.610 --> 00:33:41.550 align:middle line:84%
Mavens love connecting
you to the right resources

00:33:41.550 --> 00:33:46.290 align:middle line:84%
or information that you
need to make wise decisions.

00:33:46.290 --> 00:33:48.750 align:middle line:84%
The third group are
called persuaders.

00:33:48.750 --> 00:33:51.390 align:middle line:84%
This group is really
good at sales, but not

00:33:51.390 --> 00:33:53.850 align:middle line:84%
from a place of
agenda or pushiness.

00:33:53.850 --> 00:33:57.150 align:middle line:84%
They truly want to serve
people, and they really

00:33:57.150 --> 00:34:00.930 align:middle line:84%
like to help people find
solutions to their problems.

00:34:00.930 --> 00:34:03.310 align:middle line:84%
They may represent a
certain product or service,

00:34:03.310 --> 00:34:07.100 align:middle line:84%
and this is something that
they usually truly believe in.

00:34:07.100 --> 00:34:09.150 align:middle line:84%
And then they're really
good at persuading

00:34:09.150 --> 00:34:13.850 align:middle line:84%
and helping people make the
right decision to invest.

00:34:13.850 --> 00:34:16.699 align:middle line:84%
Now, Gladwell talks about all
of this from the perspective

00:34:16.699 --> 00:34:18.260 align:middle line:90%
of marketing and business.

00:34:18.260 --> 00:34:20.389 align:middle line:84%
But we can take
these same principles

00:34:20.389 --> 00:34:22.639 align:middle line:84%
